latestPosts.caption:
Sky ❤️
I will always be a “look at the sky, it’s so beautiful” girlie !
Even if the sky looks exactly the same everyday, there is beauty in the way the clouds arrange themselves, the way the sky color changes almost throughout the entire day, the way birds commute and communicate among themselves, the way the wind feels different with the different sky colours, the way the flowers bloom and then shrivel up during the night, while some bloom in the moon light ! 
Nature is beautiful ! 
And so is this song !
.

latestPosts.caption:
Hi my beauty Girlies and if guys are watching this, take notes for your girlfriends!

I have been struggling when it comes to wearing liquid lipsticks because they’re really expensive and on top of that the entire experience of wearing a good liquid lipstick comes crashing because most of them are too drying. 

I then switched to bullet lipsticks again, obviously these have to be reapplied because we alp know that we end up eating them with our food somehow !!

I came across this liquid lip cream on a random day when I was exploring a mall with my friend and I just fell in love with the shade. I was again scared about the fact that this was liquid lipstick and could be drying, but to my surprise it was light, a bit creamy and beautiful!

Then what ?! I bought it 🎀 

Thought of sharing this with y’all ! Happy Sunday !

Grateful to be able to breathe, Stay safe y’all ❤️
.
